C...PYLOGO
C...Writes a logo for the program.
 
      SUBROUTINE PYLOGO
 
C...Double precision and integer declarations.
      IMPLICIT DOUBLE PRECISION(A-H, O-Z)
      INTEGER PYK,PYCHGE,PYCOMP
C...Parameter for length of information block.
