C...PYNULL
C...Resets bin contents of a histogram.
 
      SUBROUTINE PYNULL(ID)
 
C...Double precision declaration.
      IMPLICIT DOUBLE PRECISION(A-H, O-Z)
C...Commonblock.
      COMMON/PYBINS/IHIST(4),INDX(1000),BIN(20000)
